learning_outcomes.en:
After completing the course the students will be able to
- hold a conversation on everyday topics without preparation;
- use simple language structures to describe their studies, experience and life;
- explain/justify their points of view;
- talk about what they have heard or seen if the subject is familiar to them;
- get the gist of recorded audio materials that are of interest to them;
- undestand simple conversations by native speakers
- understand the main idea of radio and TV broadcasts that are on everyday topics.
